name: I'dBuyIt.At
tag_list: shopping, shop, best-buy, best-price, buy-online, shop-online, online-shopping, buy, buying-online, find-me-the-best-price
overview:
Name your price for stuff you want. Pick an item, set your price, get offers, & save money.

I’dBuyIt.At is all about getting a great deal. If you’ve ever tried looking for deals while shopping online, you know that it’s like looking for a needle in a haystack. It takes a while, wastes time, and you always miss out because the deal’s expired or the item’s out of stock.

With I’dBuyIt.At, flip everything the other way: you simply pick the item you want to buy, name your price, and get a decent deal. In other words, you get to stop looking for deals and start making your own.

No coupons, no deals, no mess. You want and buy at a great price.
